{"tid":2286771,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加州州長簽行政命令擅自向選民分發郵寄選票 法院裁定違憲","createTime":"2020-11-15T09:04:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-15T13:41:41.000Z","uid":337052,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1cb064c66b10521668e3bc94a7f5c1ec0d33674a","tid":2286771,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T09:04:57.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">加州州長簽行政命令擅自向選民分發郵寄選票 法院裁定違憲</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n2020/11/15 15:44<br />\n〔編譯孫宇青／綜合報導〕<span class=\"red\">美國民主黨籍加利福尼亞州州長紐森（Gavin Newsom）6月簽署行政命令，向所有登記選民分發郵寄選票，遭2名州眾議員控告越權立法。法院13日裁定紐森違憲，指即使在疫情期間，州長也無權修改或改變現行選舉法。<br />\n</span><br />\n《福斯新聞》（Fox News）報導，紐森6月3日簽署行政命令，搶在州議會通過類似法令之前，率先援引「加州緊急服務法」（下稱緊急法），向全州登記選民分發郵寄選票，遭州眾議員蓋拉格（James Gallagher）和基利（Kevin Kiley）控告，指修法屬立法機關職責，紐森的行動相當危險。<br />\n<br />\n加州沙特郡（Sutter County）高等法院法官赫克曼（Sarah Heckman）13日作出判決，指即使處於疫情期間，「緊急法」並未賦予州長改變現行法律的權力，這屬於立法機關的權力，其越權行為恐怕會立下不良先例，禁止他今後再以「緊急法」更改任何現行法律。<br />\n<br />\n紐森辦公室則反駁道，州長有權在緊急情況下，發布命令保護居民，不同意限制州長的緊急權力，同時也強調，此一裁決並不影響計票結果。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3352451\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3352451&d=eSah%2B3q63CE7QW%2BLxhD4%2BFSbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=7194f3e4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3352451&h=e460d739\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3352451</a>"},{"pid":"15c7e18cb0741390140062c8fd6434ea6c6c56b7","tid":2286771,"uid":337052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T09:05:46.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">California judge rules Gov. Gavin Newsom overstepped authority with mail ballot order</span></strong><br />\nThe ruling prevents Newsom from changing existing law under any circumstance<br />\nBy Peter Aitken | Fox News<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.foxnews.com/politics/california-judge-gavin-newsom-authority-mail-ballot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fcalifornia-judge-gavin-newsom-authority-mail-ballot&d=eSah%2B3q63CE7QW%2BLxhD4%2BFSbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=4efc8aad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fcalifornia-judge-gavin-newsom-authority-mail-ballot&h=1dac02b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.foxnews.com/politics/california-judge-gavin-newsom-authority-mail-ballot</a>"},{"pid":"957172707b33bd838ff2a340c8f1833132737934","tid":2286771,"uid":110456,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T09:07:34.000Z","msg":"此一裁決並不影響計票結果<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔係由法庭決定嘅咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4bc154fb2b6704fcdd8c581b7abd0d49506168a","tid":2286771,"uid":337052,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"957172707b33bd838ff2a340c8f1833132737934","tid":2286771,"uid":110456,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T09:07:34.000Z","msg":"此一裁決並不影響計票結果<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔係由法庭決定嘅咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T09:08:50.000Z","msg":"可以提起選舉無效訴訟"},{"pid":"52283e12e6b730e530b724f7513c8c7592200093","tid":2286771,"uid":290314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T09:22:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"340ee44a442c6f6ff27cc676a100ca72e1d83dd2","tid":2286771,"uid":70013,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"957172707b33bd838ff2a340c8f1833132737934","tid":2286771,"uid":110456,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T09:07:34.000Z","msg":"此一裁決並不影響計票結果<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔係由法庭決定嘅咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T13:27:21.000Z","msg":"佢自己講啫<br />\n影唔影響都